    "Training is performed sequentially for resolutions in a coarse-to-fine manner.",
    "Training proceeds in two stages.",
    "The first stage begins with randomly initialized weights for both Encoder and Aligner.",
    "During the first stage, the training loss for both encoder and aligner is based on the squared difference between the images after alignment by the Aligner net, plus an elastic regularizer.",
